About this item

  • 3D Respimesh for Breathability :- Introducing the future of footwear: It's like wearing a second skin that breathes and flexes with you, offering a fit so personalized that you'll wonder if they were custom-made just for you. They're like the AC for your feet, only way more stylish!
  • Water-friendly, Vegan, Premium, Italian Faux Leather :- Embrace the future of cruelty-free luxury with our buttery-soft, Italian-inspired faux leather that not only looks good but feels even better – because being kind to animals never goes out of style.
  • Moisture-wicking Ribbed Memory foam Insole for Ultra Comfort :- Your ticket to walking on clouds! These magical marvels are like a cozy, cushiony hug for your feet. It's time to upgrade your shoe game and pamper your tootsies with these memory foam insoles – because comfort never looked so cool.
  • Anti-skid Ecotread Recycled Rubber outsoles :- Our revolutionary outsoles: the ultimate fusion of style and substance! Crafted from the toughest recycled rubber, these outsoles are eco-friendly and built to last, so you can stride with confidence while reducing your carbon footprint.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
